# Navigate Peptides — Content & SEO Strategy

## The Constraint That Changes Everything

The payment processor explicitly prohibits: "No blogs, FAQs, or SEO terms that imply personal or human use." LegitScript is unavailable for RUO vendors, blocking Google Ads and Meta Ads. **Organic SEO with purely scientific content is the only scalable traffic channel.**

