## SEO Strategy

### Target Keywords
- "peptide sciences alternative" — massive post-shutdown volume
- "buy BPC-157 online" / "research peptides for sale"
- "peptide COA verification" / "HPLC peptide testing"
- "best peptide vendor 2026"
- Compound-specific: "[compound name] research peptide"

### Technical SEO
- SSR/SSG for all public pages
- Product schema, Article schema, Organization schema, BreadcrumbList, FAQPage
- XML sitemap, canonical URLs, Open Graph tags
- Page speed: Lighthouse >90, LCP <2.5s

### Link Building Opportunity
Peptide Sciences had 1.5M monthly visits and DA 41 before shutdown. Thousands of broken links point to their product pages. Broken link building against PS's backlink profile is the highest-ROI SEO tactic available.

### Content Types That Rank (Within Compliance)
- Individual compound pages (sequence, MW, CAS, research citations)
- Scientific comparison tables (by mechanism, molecular target)
- COA documentation and methodology pages
- Peptide purity analysis and verification guides
- Industry/regulatory analysis (factual, no consumer framing)

